to clamped with n as number, low as number, high as number giving number:
    if n is less than low:
        give back low
    if n is more than high:
        give back high
    give back n

to between with n as number, low as number, high as number giving yesno:
    give back n is at least low and n is at most high

to percent_of with part as number, whole as number giving decimal:
    give back (decimal from part) divided by (decimal from whole) times 100.0
